snippet.textDisplay: Usyk vs Chisora is a really interesting match. I expect Chisora to turn up (he doesn't always) and it will be interesting to see how Usyk copes with a legit big heavyweight. Chisora is fairly heavy handed (OK, he's no Earnie Shavers) but he can punch and that'll be a proper test for Usyk too. I've always felt Usyk's footwork will be a proper handful for Fury who will be meeting someone on his skill level for the first time. I wondered however, how Usyk would do against a big heavyweight who can punch. I guess we're going to find out.
